0x526FEE31.name: NETWORK_GET_ENTITY_OWNER

params.name: entity
params.description: The entity to get the owner for.

0x526FEE31.description: Returns the owner ID of the specified entity.
0x526FEE31.resultsDescription: On the server, the server ID of the entity owner. On the client, returns the player/slot ID of the entity owner.
